<verse number="8" style="v" />For the sake of my brothers and my friends</para>

<para style="q1">I will say, "May there be peace within you."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />For the sake of the house of Yahweh our God,</para>

<para style="q1">I will seek good for you.</para>
